794
00:45:49,997 --> 00:45:53,709
<i>Scottie Pippen continues to play
perfect basketball.</i>

795
00:45:57,963 --> 00:46:00,758
<i>♪ Black flowers blossom ♪</i>

796
00:46:00,841 --> 00:46:02,259
Michael has always been

797
00:46:02,342 --> 00:46:04,678
pretty close to the vest
with his feelings.

798
00:46:06,430 --> 00:46:09,892
He was holding it together
for the entire family.

799
00:46:09,975 --> 00:46:13,312
He was so strong
for the rest of us.

800
00:46:13,395 --> 00:46:16,356
He won't allow you to see the emptiness.

801
00:46:16,440 --> 00:46:20,277
He said, "Mom, I know he's there.
He's watching. He sees."

802
00:46:20,778 --> 00:46:23,113
<i>♪ Water is my eye ♪</i>

803
00:46:23,197 --> 00:46:25,199
<i>Seven-year-old Jeffrey Jordan</i>

804
00:46:25,282 --> 00:46:27,910
<i>holding up a Happy Father's Day sign.</i>

805
00:46:29,536 --> 00:46:32,456
<i>The Bulls have a 15-point lead.</i>

806
00:46:35,584 --> 00:46:38,212
<i>This has just become
a clinic for Chicago.</i>

807
00:46:38,295 --> 00:46:43,050
<i>George Karl forced to call a timeout.
Things falling apart for Seattle.</i>

808
00:46:43,133 --> 00:46:45,427
<i>87-75.</i>

809
00:46:46,887 --> 00:46:48,263
<i>We're in the final seconds.</i>

810
00:46:48,806 --> 00:46:51,892
<i>The Chicago Bulls have won</i>

811
00:46:52,601 --> 00:46:57,731
<i>the '95-'96 NBA Championship.</i>

812
00:46:57,815 --> 00:47:00,651
<i>Make it four in six years.</i>

813
00:47:02,152 --> 00:47:04,863
Michael, I know that
the first one was sweet,

814
00:47:04,947 --> 00:47:06,657
but how much sweeter was this one?

815
00:47:07,533 --> 00:47:10,410
Well, you know,
I can't even put it in words.

816
00:47:11,161 --> 00:47:13,163
On Father's Day, what it means to me.

817
00:47:15,249 --> 00:47:16,500
I know he's watching.

818
00:47:17,042 --> 00:47:19,586
To my wife, and to my kids, to my mother,

819
00:47:19,670 --> 00:47:22,631
my brothers and sisters,
this is for Daddy.

820
00:47:22,714 --> 00:47:24,258
I'm very happy right now.

821
00:47:24,341 --> 00:47:27,719
<i>♪ You're stumbling into all ♪</i>

822
00:47:30,931 --> 00:47:34,601
<i>♪ Stumbling into all ♪</i>

823
00:47:55,956 --> 00:47:58,250
<i>We're just over 40 minutes
